data.description: Here is your opportunity to own this beautiful 5 bedroom, 4 and 1/2 bathrooms home in Hidden Valley Lake. This nearly 4000 square foot home offers to much room to grow. 3 of the bedrooms upstairs  feature adjoining baths. There is plenty of room to entertain in the home and on the outside with the 2 lot included in this sale. Take advantage of the walking trails, lakes for swimming, fishing and boating, the tennis courts, the pool and the golf course located in Hidden Valley Lake.
